::Terragator wakes up on the Beast Wars world.  He has no idea how he got 
there::
Terragator: Strange, this can't be Cybertron . . . but it does not look like 
any earth I've ever been to.  I'd better create an alt form based on the 
locals.
Terragator's Computer: Warning scanners have been damaged.
Terragator: Just do it!
Terragator's Computer: Agnowledged
::A snapping turtle and an alligator are fighting.  The scanner passes right 
over them::
Terragator: Beast Mode!
::He transforms into his turtle/alligator mode::
Terragator: Exellent, yes!  Terragator, TERRORIZE!
::He transforms into his new robot mode.  He was going to like it here, yes::
